<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>My Portfolio</title>
<style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background: #0f172a;
    color: white;
}
header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: #020617;
}
section {
    padding: 40px;
}
h1, h2 {
    color: #38bdf8;
}
.projects {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}
.card {
    background: #1e293b;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}
footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #020617;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Your Name</h1>
    <p>Graphic Designer & Web Developer</p>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I am a Computer Science graduate with skills in graphic design and web development. I build clean and responsive designs.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <p>HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Figma, Photoshop, Canva</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Business Website</h3>
            <p>Responsive website built with HTML, CSS, JS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
            <p>Personal portfolio project</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Logo Design</h3>
            <p>Brand identity and logo creation</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: your@email.com</p>
    <p>Phone: 08000000000</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Your Name</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
